{"tid":441402,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"《我們仨》讀後感","createTime":"2017-10-19T15:21:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-20T07:16:33.000Z","uid":81190,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"afbcaf2e798e9b77e60aa0f58a65f31841ba1d4b","tid":441402,"uid":81190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T15:21:12.000Z","msg":"屌你老味，錢鍾書都on撚柒鳩鳩<br />\n日日讀書讀書，成個濕鳩書呆子咁<br />\n又要成日整爛人地啲嘢<br />\n整爛完又要問老婆點整<br />\n除咗讀書叻都唔知有乜撚嘢用<br />\n楊絳又係，好嫁唔嫁嫁個書呆子<br />\n以佢咁嘅才能，醒水識時務落嚟香港<br />\n當時政府多數俾個教席佢喺大學度教<br />\n個個月人工咁多，生活應該唔成問題<br />\n喺大陸，又要被人鬥，又要冇錢，又冇社經地位<br />\n都唔知留喺大陸做乜<br />\n讀書讀書，讀到傻撚咗呀"},{"pid":"57ed2f17c01a6de8e72f723b8c5edd29aa33461b","tid":441402,"uid":81190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T15:27:57.000Z","msg":"人呢"},{"pid":"7bbd09b5d7b7b89e4edbce13ee6a2369eeadf441","tid":441402,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T15:28:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72679825b6a468f27c935e70302d018d0a09e325","tid":441402,"uid":51978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T15:29:41.000Z","msg":"書呆子都叻過你一百倍啦"},{"pid":"5005f4c38c3314bdc750b6b4824598bea98e5aa1","tid":441402,"uid":81190,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T15:39:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>書呆子都叻過你一百倍啦</blockquote><br />\n佢除咗識讀書叻仲有咩叻<br />\n揾錢叻？睇時勢？<br />\n好似冇"},{"pid":"72ca9abfe3197ee5e127bfc7fadb278bff95d643","tid":441402,"uid":81190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T15:56:01.000Z","msg":"人呢，入嚟啦<br />\n入嚟討論吓錢鍾書啦呢條友啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點解唔討論呀"},{"pid":"d55bec7b6aa298b90b8c2378b495627ac5389405","tid":441402,"uid":81190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T15:59:41.000Z","msg":"屌吓我都好呀"},{"pid":"13305120c749e3a825410b670a17d171cd95f58d","tid":441402,"uid":110892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cite